data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Temple! This spacious residence boasts four bedrooms, two baths, and a range of desirable features that make it the perfect blend of comfort and functionality.

As you step inside, the open layout ensures that the kitchen seamlessly flows into the adjoining areas, making it an ideal space for entertaining or family gatherings. Recessed lighting in the kitchen immediately catches your eye, creating a bright and welcoming atmosphere. The kitchen is equipped with an electric stove that can easily be converted to gas.

The primary bedroom is a true retreat, isolated from the rest of the house for added privacy. The attached large bathroom  features a spacious place for your daily routine.

The three additional bedrooms are adorned with new laminate flooring, creating a cohesive and stylish look throughout the home. This durable and easy-to-maintain flooring enhances the overall aesthetic and provides a comfortable foundation for every room.

The home's infrastructure has been thoughtfully updated, with a newer AC system ensuring your comfort year-round. A new roof, installed in 2020, adds to the property's longevity and gives you peace of mind. 

Step outside into the backyard, where you'll discover a screened-in patio, perfect for enjoying the outdoors without the hassle of insects. Additionally, a sizable 21x12 garage with electricity provides ample storage space or can be utilized as a workshop, catering to a variety of needs.

This wonderful home is located in  a prime area in the heart of Temple ensures convenient access to local amenities, schools, and parks. Don't miss the opportunity to make this well cared-for property your new home sweet home!
